com.citytechinc.cq.component.annotations
Annotation Type Component

@Retention(value=CLASS)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface Component

The Component marks your class as a CQ Component. Tools will use this annotation to determine whether to perform an operation on the class or not.

          The jcr:title of the Component
